	<assemblage label="whats-a-de-wrap-up">
		<title><e component="emoji">üì§</e> Wrap-Up</title>
		<p>
			<paragraphs label="whats-a-de-takeaways">
				<title><e component="emoji">üóùÔ∏è</e> Key Takeaways..</title>
				<ul marker="square">
					<li>A differential equation involves an unknown function and at least one of its derivatives.</li>
					<li>It must contain an equals sign to be considered an equation.</li>
					<li>Differential equations are a natural extension of algebra and calculus.</li>
					<li>Notation varies by context but generally falls into prime, Leibniz, or dot notation.</li>
				</ul>
			</paragraphs>
		</p>
	</assemblage>
